		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well you can't use the official markings unless your game is approved, so in that case it'd probably be best to just give a short content warning like modern games do during start up. 
<br />
<br />My game concept is quite violent for NES standards and contains "mature themes", that's really part of the fun of unlicensed games, getting away with whatever content you want.

		

